---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/sections/Section.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/sections/CTABanner.astro';
import Card from '../../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../../components/animation/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Just Curious? Start Here | IBC Academy"
  description="New to the Infinite Banking Concept? Skeptical? Good. This 6-article journey will help you see your financial blind spots - no sales pitch, just clarity."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Section background="cream">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-eyebrow">For the Curious & Skeptical</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title">You've Heard About "Infinite Banking." <br />You're Not Sure What to Think.</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          Maybe someone mentioned it at a dinner party. Maybe you saw a YouTube video that sounded too good to be true. Maybe a friend keeps talking about "being your own banker" and you're wondering if they've joined a cult.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          Good. Skepticism is healthy. It means you're paying attention.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          This isn't a sales page. There's no pitch at the end. Just six short articles designed to help you see something most people miss about how money actually works.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- What This Is (And Isn't) -->
  <Section title="What This Journey Is (And Isn't)">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="clarity-content">
        <div class="clarity-grid">
          <div class="clarity-box">
            <h3 class="clarity-heading is-not">This is NOT:</h3>
            <ul class="clarity-list">
              <li>A get-rich-quick scheme</li>
              <li>A "hack" or "loophole"</li>
              <li>A way to beat the stock market</li>
              <li>Something that works for everyone</li>
              <li>A replacement for thinking critically</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="clarity-box">
            <h3 class="clarity-heading is-yes">This IS:</h3>
            <ul class="clarity-list">
              <li>A different way of looking at money</li>
              <li>Questions you've probably never asked</li>
              <li>Simple concepts explained plainly</li>
              <li>A framework for thinking, not a product</li>
              <li>Free education with no strings attached</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="clarity-footer">
          By the end, you'll either see something you didn't see before — or you'll conclude this isn't for you. Both are perfectly valid outcomes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- The 6 Articles -->
  <Section title="Your 6-Article Journey" subtitle="Each article takes about 5-7 minutes to read. No jargon. No math. Just ideas." background="cream">
    <div class="journey-grid">
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={0}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/just-curious-01-where-does-money-go" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">01</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">Where Does Your Money Actually Go?</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">$2–5 million flows through your hands in a lifetime. Have you ever stopped to ask where it all ends up?</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={100}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/just-curious-02-silent-partner" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">02</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The Silent Partner in Every Purchase</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">Every time you finance something, someone else profits. The average American pays $400,000+ in lifetime interest. Who's collecting it?</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={200}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/just-curious-03-good-debt-bad-debt" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">03</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The Lie About "Good Debt" and "Bad Debt"</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">Dave Ramsey says all debt is evil. The leverage crowd says debt is a tool. Both are missing the real question.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={300}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/just-curious-04-what-banks-do" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">04</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">What Banks Actually Do (And Why They're Rich)</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">You deposit at 0.5%. They lend at 7%. You're not the customer — you're the product. Here's how it actually works.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={400}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/just-curious-05-question-about-retirement" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">05</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The Question Nobody Asks About Retirement</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">Can you touch your retirement money tomorrow? You traded access for tax benefits. Is that a deal you'd take again?</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={500}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/just-curious-06-what-if-you-were-bank" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">06</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">What If You Were the Bank?</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">The question that changes everything. A forester named Nelson Nash spent decades figuring out the answer.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <Section title="Why Bother?">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="why-content">
        <p class="why-text">
          Here's a question worth sitting with:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="why-quote">
          "You finance everything you buy. Either you pay interest to someone else, or you give up the interest you could have earned."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="why-attribution">— Nelson Nash, creator of the Infinite Banking Concept</p>
        <p class="why-text">
          Read that again. There's no third option.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          Most people spend their entire lives focused on earning more and investing better — while ignoring the 30+ cents of every dollar that bleeds out through the financing function of their lives.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          This isn't about selling you anything. It's about helping you see something that's been invisible. What you do with that knowledge is up to you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <Section background="cream">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Start?</h2>
        <p class="cta-text">
          Article 1 takes about 5 minutes. No signup required. No email capture. Just read.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-button">
          <Button variant="primary" size="lg" href="/learn/articles/just-curious-01-where-does-money-go">
            Begin Article 1 →
          </Button>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">
          Still not sure? That's fine. Bookmark this page and come back when you're ready. The information will still be here.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- Final Note -->
  <CTABanner
    heading="Have Questions?"
    description="Join our free community where 500+ people are learning together. Ask anything. No pressure."
    buttonText="Join the Conversation"
    buttonHref="https://skool.com/ibc-academy"
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold, #C9A962);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .hero-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .hero-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Clarity Section */
  .clarity-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .clarity-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .clarity-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .clarity-box {
    background: var(--color-cream, #FAF9F6);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .clarity-heading {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .clarity-heading.is-not {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
  }

  .clarity-heading.is-yes {
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
  }

  .clarity-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .clarity-list li {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .clarity-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-gold, #C9A962);
  }

  .clarity-footer {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Journey Section */
  .journey-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .journey-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .journey-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .journey-card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .journey-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .journey-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.12);
  }

  .journey-number {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gold, #C9A962);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .journey-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .journey-desc {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Why Section */
  .why-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .why-quote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold, #C9A962);
    text-align: left;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .why-quote {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
  }

  .why-attribution {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .why-attribution {
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-button {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
